snippet.title: Living Ball (DOS, 1995)
snippet.description:
One of, if not the, largest pinball game ever created. The first world alone features 99 levels, along with two smaller ones. In total, that's 165 screen heights worth of pinball table, guaranteed to keep all pinball fans busy for a while. The game features an adventure mode, where you have to conquer each world and their empresses.

No copyright infringements intended. All audio, images and video content belongs to their original creators! Please contact us if there's a video issue!

Recorded by Coreus
